data.description: Welcome to Cannie Phillips Rd! Walk inside to find an open living and dining area. Nice-sized kitchen with a pantry! Huge laundry room too! New engineered hardwood floors throughout the living area. Spacious bedrooms, and amazing one acre level lot! The current owners have also had the crawlspace water proofed and encapsulated!  This home is perfectly priced and great for private country living with all the convenience of the nearby town of Sumiton. And just about 3 miles from Bevill state, shopping and restaurants!
